name: Black Vintage Stone Earrings

Beautiful black vintage glass stones in a brass vintage setting. 

Choose between sweet little bows or a simple oval lever back. 

These are the perfect pair of earrings to dress up your look!

name: -Be Still- Bracelet
description:
An Antique Bronze Charm hand stamped with the words "Be Still"
Bracelet is made with Aqua Blue Vintage Glass Beads and a pretty little peach rose. 

Simple, Beautiful, Meaningful.

name: Charm Bracelet
description:
A unique and beautiful charm bracelet that truly shines. 

Gorgeous cameo charm, peach enamel heart, a diamond drop stone, and little cream rose hang from a gold link bracelet. 

7 1/2 inches in length. 
Can be made shorter or longer.

name: Vintage Cream Bloom on Aqua Blue Glass Bead Chain
description:
A small antiqued bronze bird, connects a gorgeous detailed cream bloom between a double layer of vintage aqua blue glass beads and an antiqued bronze chain. lobster clasp closure. 

This necklace is beautiful and unique! 

Necklace hangs approximately 25 inches long.

name: Vintage Double Heart Ring
description:
vintage brass double heart ring 
Adjustable to fit your finger just right, or wear it at your knuckle to change things up a little. 

This ring is simply perfect and one of my personal favorites. 
I wear mine every single day!

name: Tiny Initial Necklace
description:
Two Vintage brass charms hand stamped with custom initial of your choice. 

Chain is 14k gold filled with 14k gold spring clasp and jump rings. 
Necklace measures approx 18inches in length

Please include which two initials you would like, in the notes at checkout. 

If you'd like to add more charms to include your children or those special to you, you can do so here:
http://www.splendorshop.com/category/add-on


NOTE: Brass may take on a deeper tone over time, 
brighten with jewelry polish cloth or lemon water if desired

Love these!
